Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.72,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}I've still got a lot of years ahead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:35.72,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}{\alpha&HFF&}To just erase these fee{\alpha&H00&}lings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:35.68,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}{\alpha&HFF&}To just erase {\alpha&H00&}these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.63,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}To just erase these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:38.72,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}I want to go back and finish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:42.35,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}The things that I've yet to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:58.62,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,489)}I was supposed to be chasing after my ongoing dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:04.96,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Yet I faltered over others while walking this thin, winding path.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.13,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's not that I want to return to those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:11.63,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm searching for the sky I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:13.30,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don't make that sad face, as if you've fallen victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:18.51,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}As if you want people to pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:20.22,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tears aren't the end of your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.89,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You have to bear them painfully, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.56,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Who are you waiting for in the maze of emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:25.23,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where you can't even see the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:27.02,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want to blurt it out more justly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.77,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just like how I wrote it in my white notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.44,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What do you want to run from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.07,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That thing called "reality"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:35.40,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I just want to scream out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.82,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"I'm only living to fulfill my wish." Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:42.95,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}I can't take the safe way out of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.75,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't even have a place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.04,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm always thankful for everyone's kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:52.42,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's why I want to become stronger. (I'm on the way)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.38,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is reminding me of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.63,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}This pain is all right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.72,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(489,0)}{\blur3}この想いを　消してしまうには
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:35.72,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(644,652)}{\alpha&HFF&}まだ人生長いでし{\alpha&H00&}ょ？
