Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:14.06,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Say, the sky we saw that day, the scarlet sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:19.27,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do you remember it from that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:25.19,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We made a promise and a vow while the early summer wind circled us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:29.45,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}And we clung close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:38.50,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Your forced smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:43.88,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Holds elongated shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:53.14,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}I pretend not to notice and continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.65,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,480)}All the while waiting for you to deliver some news at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:11.03,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Empty nights, mornings that will never arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:15.79,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I could see them from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:21.42,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Say, the sky we saw that day, the scarlet sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:26.34,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm sure you'll remember it one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:32.18,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}While holding the promise we couldn't keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:36.43,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}We take our first steps down our own paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:14.06,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,0)}{\blur3}あの日見た空　茜色の空を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:19.27,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ねえ　君は覚えていますか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:25.19,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}約束　契り　初夏の風が包む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:29.45,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}二人　寄り添った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:38.50,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}無理な笑顔の裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:43.88,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伸びた影をかくまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:53.14,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}だから　気づかぬふり　再生を選ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.65,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,480)}テーブルの上の　震えない知らせ　待ち続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:11.03,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}空白の夜も　来るはずのない朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:15.79,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}全部わかってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:21.42,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}あの日見た空　茜色の空を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:26.34,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ねえ　 いつか思い出すでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:32.18,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果たせなかった　約束を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:36.43,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}二人　歩き出す
